FBIS4-7502 "dreeu063_i_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-063 Daily Report 1 Apr 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA Cease-Fire Agreement Reached in Bihac Region Cease-Fire Agreement Reached in Bihac Region Further on Cease-Fire AU0104084194 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network in Serbo-Croatian 0800 GMT 1 Apr 94 AU0104084194 Sarajevo Radio Bosnia-Herzegovina Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] We have just received a report saying the following: An agreement has been reached between Karadzic's Serbs and Bosniaks on the cessation of fighting in the Bihac region, UNPROFOR [UN Protection Forces] has reported. The agreement envisages the separation of forces, buffer zones, withdrawal of heavy weapons, the possibility of supervision by the UN forces, freedom of movement for international humanitarian organizations, and foundation of a joint commission.
